CustomField.description: Sets whether the menu and sub menu items are processed for a specific version of the application. If a value is selected ie V001 then this menu or sub menu item will be returned in the initial query to return to the user - but this will be further reduced to only the Profile Menu Items that correspond to the Community Profile
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Sets whether the menu and sub menu items are processed for a specific version of the application. If a value is selected ie V001 then this menu or sub menu item will be returned in the initial query to return to the user - but this will be further reduced
CustomField.label: Available in Version
